    "title_en": "Deliverable-Compute Bottleneck Radar",
    "title_zh": "AI 算力交付瓶頸雷達",
    "subtitle_en": "TSMC AI capacity is necessary but NOT sufficient. Real deliverable compute is set by the WEAKEST link across the whole chain — front-end wafer, CoWoS/SoIC packaging, HBM, ABF substrate, grid power, cooling/water, optics. Every link is converted to one common unit (B200/GB200-class accelerator-equivalents per quarter), then we take the minimum. The question this board answers: is TSMC the binding constraint? If not, which link is, by how much, and when does the bottleneck migrate?",
    "subtitle_zh": "台積電 AI 產能是必要、但非充分條件。真正可交付的算力由整條鏈的「最弱一環」決定——前段晶圓、CoWoS/SoIC 封裝、HBM、ABF 基板、電網電力、散熱/水、光通訊。每一環都換算成同一個共同單位（等效 B200/GB200-class 加速器／季），再取最小值。本平台回答：台積電是不是綁定約束？若不是，最弱的是哪一環、差多少、瓶頸何時移轉？",
    "unit_en": "Common unit = B200/GB200-class accelerator-equivalents per quarter (EA/qtr). Deliverable compute = MIN across links (Liebig's law of the minimum / theory of constraints).",
    "unit_zh": "共同單位 = 等效 B200/GB200-class 加速器／季（EA/qtr）。可交付算力 = 各環節取最小值（Liebig 最小值定律／約束理論）。",
    "domain_caveat_en": "Every number below is a FLAGGED SEED value pre-filled by Claude for the foundry capacity-planning team to correct. They are deliberately dated, sourced and tier-graded — the platform's job is to make these shifting assumptions visible and to find the binding link, not to assert the numbers as truth. Replace seeds with primary capacity guidance (TSMC CoWoS, SK Hynix/Micron HBM bit growth, grid interconnection queues) as it lands.",
    "domain_caveat_zh": "以下每個數字都是 Claude 預填、標示為待校正的種子假設值，供晶圓代工產能規劃團隊修正。它們刻意帶日期、來源與證據分級——平台的目的是讓這些會漂移的假設「可見」並找出綁定環節，而非主張其為真。請隨一手產能指引（TSMC CoWoS、SK Hynix／Micron HBM bit 成長、電網併網排隊）到位後替換種子值。"
  },
